<section id="content">

<blockquote>
	<q>Art should never try to be popular. The public should try to make itself artistic.</q>
	<cite><a href="/author/171">Oscar Wilde</a></cite>
	<footer>contributed by <a href="/contributor/430">Gerry O'Beirne</a></footer>
</blockquote>

